QuestData.Title: Valley of the Four Winds
QuestData.Description: Yarr, the Jade Forest be goin through some violent reconstruction, but the Valley of the Four Winds is ripe for explorin. Talk with me when ye be ready to go and I can give ye a ride ta where ya need to go. Talk to me cohort on the other side 'ta get some equipment to aid ya on yer journey.
QuestData.LogDescription: Teleport to Valley of the Four Winds and speak to Private Tim P. O'Rary.

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Private Tim P. O'Rary in Valley of the Four Winds
